subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution.
Bryopesanser tonsillorum
n. sp.
is widespread in its distribution, being found on the coast of Ghana , West Africa (
Cook 1968
), Sri Lanka (
Thornely 1905
), Indonesia (
Harmer 1957
), Philippines (
Canu & Bassler 1929
), and east to Isla Gorgona, off the Pacific coast of Colombia (
Hastings 1930
).
